snippet.title: Roma and Diana Pretend Play with Nail polish for kids
snippet.description:
Roma and Diana Pretend Play with color Nail polish. Diana wanted to make herself a manicure with baby nail polish. But the little girl did not succeed. Then Roma helped her. Hilarious video for children.
